    • asUnmodifiable

      MutableDoubleBooleanMap asUnmodifiable()
      Returns an unmodifiable view of this map, delegating all read-only operations to this map and throwing an UnsupportedOperationException for all mutating operations. This avoids the overhead of copying the map when calling DoubleBooleanMap.toImmutable() while still providing immutability.
